16
00:00:55,230 --> 00:00:57,180
bottleneck and needed more automation.

17
00:00:57,949 --> 00:01:00,910
And after a series of discussion,
they brought in a specific tool

18
00:01:01,449 --> 00:01:02,730
and it actually resolved the speed.

19
00:01:03,389 --> 00:01:07,449
They could generate mi-migration
faster than before and scaffold

20
00:01:07,529 --> 00:01:11,269
schemas better than before and
